short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Click an emoji, let Eden AI comment on any webpages with your own attitude

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
AI powered social plugin. Click on emojis on any webpages to show your attitude. AI will summarize the page and create interesting comments tailored to your interest. Roast your friend, love a webpage, or simply drop a comment!
